summary: A simple mod that makes Xenius\' Obscuuri race nude.
descriptionHtml:
Please excuse the poor screenshot quality, I used a low-end machine to take it.  Feel free to upload your own better ones!

Note: As with the original mod, the screenshot does not reflect the actual skin tone.  See the user image section on the original mod for what the actual skin tone is like.  I already have a mod completed that makes the skin tone look like my screenshot, but am waiting on Xenius\' approval to release it.

Requirements: 
The Xenius\' wonderful original mod: 
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/mods/26842

All credits go to Xenius, this is a simple mesh edit for people who do not have a mesh editor.
author: Damienblair
